Interface Stimulus

All Superinterfaces:

public interface Stimulus
extends ModelElement, Stimulus

A representation of the model object 'Stimulus'.

The following features are supported:

  • Argument
  • Sender
  • Receiver
  • Communication Link
  • Dispatch Action
  • Played Role
  • Interaction Instance Set
